The paper is about iris image datasets and their use in biometric evaluations, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of an LG 2200 iris imaging system for image acquisition suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.MM) and pattern recognition (cs.LG). Finally, the dataset itself is related to iris recognition (cs.IR).
